    <text>Status Legend:
• running (Green): Service is active and running
• stopped (Red): Service is inactive/stopped
• starting (Orange): Service is in the process of starting
• stopping (Orange): Service is in the process of stopping
• not-found (Gray): Service is not found or not loaded
• unknown (Black): Service state is unknown

Control Instructions:
• Start/Stop Button: Click to start (green) or stop (red) the service
• Reset Failed Button: Click to reset the failed state of the service
• Status updates automatically every second
• Confirmation dialogs appear before performing actions</text>
